text: I'm pushing for a strong infrastructure investment, because rural communities deserve #ABetterDeal: better jobs, better wages and a better future.

Anyone else feel like that was a uniquely long week of distractions from the White House? I think the American people would have been much better served if they had instead spent that time working with us on #ABetterDeal to deliver better jobs, better wages and a better future!

It is unfortunate that once again, in the midst of serious negotiations, @realdonaldtrump used offensive language that stokes racial tensions. Instead, I wish he would spend his time working to grow our economy, create jobs and build a better future for ALL of our families.

Hey @SpeakerRyan- Since we have to hold a do-over vote on the #GOPTaxScam, maybe we could take out the parts about raising taxes on 86M middle-class families, incentivizing companies to ship jobs overseas & kicking 13M off of their healthcare. Working families would appreciate it

The first bill I introduced this Congress called on @realDonaldTrump to release a plan to end the outsourcing of good American jobs.

But Washington Republicans delivered a gut punch to hardworking families by raising their taxes & making it easier to ship jobs overseas #TaxScam

Last week, from Washington Republicans:
-Moving forward on a #TaxScam that attacks the working class.
-Repealing #NetNeutrality which hurts small biz, entrepreneurs & consumers

Meanwhile, Democrats are fighting for #ABetterDeal for you-Better jobs, better wages & a better future
What an amazing night - congratulations to Senator-Elect Doug Jones! Now let’s get to work fighting for hardworking families across our country!

The #GOPTaxPlan puts #BillionairesFirst, giving them tax breaks that force millions of middle-class families to pay more for less.
